item.description: Hello and nice to meet you. I am an experienced engineering leader and entrepreneur with interests ranging between improving people’s lives, making business more productive, and doing that all with tech. So far I have had a career in services industry going from line roles in software engineering to team leadership, participated in three early-stage startups, built and exited out of my software services company. I love my family and enjoy spending time with them.
